The Stanbic IBTC Pension Managers Limited has restated its commitment towards a glorious retirement period for its clientele with a new state-of-the-art Customer Experience Centre, established in the Opebi area of Ikeja, Lagos.  The Director-General, National Pension Commission (PenCom), Aisha Dahir-Umar, commended the company for spreading its network to enable more Nigerians to benefit from the pension experience. 